{"tid":1309541,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"Hkcc BC vs Hku space AAELL","createTime":"2019-07-12T08:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T14:38:41.000Z","uid":279033,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2f774e08e72894a74107811a6bdd9fc0df354597","tid":1309541,"uid":279033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:50:42.000Z","msg":"朋友今年放榜<br />\nAsso嘅話應該揀邊一個好？<br />\nHKCC 中英語文傳意副學士 (BC)<br />\n定係<br />\nHKU SPACE 文科 英國語文(AAELL)<br />\nHku Space AAELL係上年先開, 所以末有數據知道升上大學嘅機率<br />\n怕會有伏<br />\n佢個人就中意文學多啲，將來想讀英文系，做編輯或者文學related 嘅野<br />\n唔知有冇人係有讀呢兩科呢？可唔可以講下大約情況係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻煩晒各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c04f32b599cd41cbdce060a5d13154bcc1651c","tid":1309541,"uid":201533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:52:39.000Z","msg":"bc啦 <br />\n不過想讀英文點解唔揀epc 要揀bc"},{"pid":"17df8f0ccb1187ab1ed9e74a2c11b628c458aca5","tid":1309541,"uid":279033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:57:16.000Z","msg":"佢排左去2nd choice, 後悔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf1bc2bc89e068ad33c6dc39b800b363780edd40","tid":1309541,"uid":279033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:38:41.000Z","msg":"Up"}]}